sentences.english: The rotation as Euler angles in degrees relative to the parent transform's rotation.
sentences.chinese: 旋轉作爲歐拉角度，相對於父級的變換旋轉角度。

sentences.english: Position of the transform relative to the parent transform.
sentences.chinese: 相對於父級的變換的位置。

sentences.english: The Structure element is the parent of the actual structure definition.
sentences.chinese: Structure元素是實際結構定義的父級。

sentences.english: An event only bubbles up the parent's chain of ancestors in the display list.
sentences.chinese: 事件在顯示列表中只向上級的父級鏈冒泡。
